@startuml architecture-externe-g4
title G4 — Architecture externe (extrait)

actor "Gestionnaire flotte" as User
component "G10 Gateway" as G10
component "G4 Coordination" as G4
component "G3 Utilisateurs" as G3
queue "Kafka\napache/kafka:3.7.0" as Kafka
component "G7 Suivi véhicule" as G7
component "G1 Billetterie" as G1
component "G5 Notifications" as G5
database "PostgreSQL" as PG

User --> G10 : HTTPS + JWT
G10 --> G4 : routes /api/g4/**
G4 --> G3 : Valider utilisateur / conducteur / rôle\n(évolution: GET /users/{id}/exists)
G4 --> PG : persistance
G7 --> Kafka : topic vehicule-positions
Kafka --> G4 : G7VehiclePositionKafkaConsumer
G4 --> G1 : HTTP / Kafka missions-lifecycle
G4 --> G5 : POST notification

@enduml
